metadata.name: Vincent van Gogh, Les Tournesols, 1888 / NFP 2
metadata.description:
Digital translation of  "Vincent van Gogh, the Sunflowers, 1888, 92 x 73 cm, Neue Pinakothek, Munich "
This NFT is used by artist Philippe Hurteau to create an actual painting, but inverted in mirror (and never minted) 
This NFT can be just printed or printed and painted in the same way as artist. 
This research is a critical and conceptual reflexion between contemporary painting, art history and digital world. More : www.hurteau.org
